{"tid":2352073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡堅：身邊「十個八個」醫生想移民","createTime":"2021-01-03T17:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T20:54:57.000Z","uid":28114,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b32f8da99ae193be1a6b872b29cecc862aac9719","tid":2352073,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T17:37:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1965927/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%94%A1%E5%A0%85-%E8%BA%AB%E9%82%8A-%E5%8D%81%E5%80%8B%E5%85%AB%E5%80%8B-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%83%B3%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1965927%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E8%2594%25A1%25E5%25A0%2585-%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E9%2582%258A-%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%2585%25AB%25E5%2580%258B-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2583%25B3%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyWXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=92444097\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1965927%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E8%2594%25A1%25E5%25A0%2585-%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E9%2582%258A-%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%2585%25AB%25E5%2580%258B-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2583%25B3%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591&h=01a08c5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1965927/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%94%A1%E5%A0%85-%E8%BA%AB%E9%82%8A-%E5%8D%81%E5%80%8B%E5%85%AB%E5%80%8B-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%83%B3%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91</a><br />\n<br />\n留港撚隨時醫生都冇得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7958ef297bef70c6ffce59d6d718eebebd05bd88","tid":2352073,"uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T17:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/525f4bc9db01283cac15f9d66e4f1f0c/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210103/_2021010308252830924.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F525f4bc9db01283cac15f9d66e4f1f0c%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210103%2F_2021010308252830924.jpg&h=d8e198e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蔡堅指，身邊「十個八個」醫生打算移民，主要同本地政治氣氛有關。<br />\n移民後如何解決餬口問題，是每個離鄉別井的人都要考慮的現實問題，特別是具備專業資格認可的人士。醫學會會長蔡堅指，早前聽聞「十個八個」醫生打算移民，主要同本地政治氣氛有關；亦有年輕的醫生表示，不少專科醫生已經預備或已經考取其他國家的執業資格試，一旦時間及條件成熟，便會馬上起行。<br />\n<br />\n醫學會會長蔡堅指，時有聽聞有香港醫護移民外國，但估計受近年香港政治氣氛轉變影響，近年移民外國的人數愈來愈多，坦言身邊有「十個八個」醫生均有移民打算。<br />\n<br />\n蔡堅又指，自己已具備在加拿大及英國的執業資格，而且有居英權，但他表示暫時未有離港移民的想法，不過隨着香港情況每況愈下，不禁讓更多港人對前景感到憂心，直言當香港的政治環境至無法承受時，不排除會離開這個地方。<br />\n<br />\n專科醫生考定外國執業試<br />\n<br />\n有不願具名的年輕醫生表示，暫時未有醫生朋友移民，但在朋友圈子中打聽到約有三十至四十名專科醫生正考慮，或已考取其他國家的執業資格，以便取得「移民入場券」，特別是有家室及子女的醫生。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">被問到哪個歐美國家會成為移民首選，他估計最多人會到移民到英國，並在當地繼續執業</span>，由於當地醫療制度跟香港相若，而且領取BNO時間較；短新加坡則要逐個個案審批，花費頗長時間；澳洲更規定海外醫生先要到當地偏遠地區執業十年，相信在這個要求下「無人想做」。"},{"pid":"a4d67f81f35680649c52db23423d3c38271752e3","tid":2352073,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T17:40:26.000Z","msg":"樓主訓撚咗幾耐？"},{"pid":"902f5787d00a34669db972f0b166be84a3f88b05","tid":2352073,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a4d67f81f35680649c52db23423d3c38271752e3","tid":2352073,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T17:40:26.000Z","msg":"樓主訓撚咗幾耐？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T17:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f15be3c250901c97a5bc815009bb33b8795be4","tid":2352073,"uid":363330,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T17:43:36.000Z","msg